snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 01 - Kioroshi Yu (1996)

DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 1: Kioroshi Yu is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1996.
